1
00:00:16,140 --> 00:00:17,980
[Kim Hyeonseo as Sung Ho]

2
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:21,020
[Jung Myeongcheol as Yoo Sehyun]

3
00:00:22,020 --> 00:00:24,000
[Kim Seonghyuk as Kwon Hyukjae]

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,010
[Jung Hyunwoong as Kim Minho]

5
00:00:34,490 --> 00:00:36,260
[Sin and Love]

6
00:00:36,260 --> 00:00:38,280
[Episode 4]

7
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:43,950
Right.

8
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,180
No.

9
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,650
Something's off about

10
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:50,120
Sehyun and Kwon Hyukjae.

11
00:01:02,450 --> 00:01:03,220
I knew it.

12
00:01:34,110 --> 00:01:34,610
[Sung Ho]

13
00:01:34,810 --> 00:01:35,520
[I...]

14
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:43,370
[Whenever I see you, I waver.]

15
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,539
[Whenever I see you, I waver.]

16
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,670
Why is there only one cup of milk?

17
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,980
[Got it.]

18
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,150
You look tired.

19
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,140
Did something happen?

20
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:16,149
I'm fine.

21
00:04:18,019 --> 00:04:19,420
I just didn't sleep well.

22
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:21,870
Don't act tough.

23
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,340
Are you sure you're OK?

24
00:04:28,380 --> 00:04:29,080
Well,

25
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:30,570
Minho told me

26
00:04:31,810 --> 00:04:33,750
you rushed out at noon.

27
00:04:36,780 --> 00:04:38,110
It's a personal matter.

28
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:46,120
I met a friend.

29
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:48,920
A friend?

30
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:51,980
Yoo Sehyun?

31
00:04:54,980 --> 00:04:55,710
Yes, well...

32
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,040
We were high school classmates.

33
00:04:58,580 --> 00:05:00,050
We just chatted a bit.

34
00:05:05,530 --> 00:05:06,390
Haven't you...

35
00:05:08,350 --> 00:05:10,410
heard about the Gangnam Palace case?

36
00:05:11,890 --> 00:05:13,280
Rumors are just rumors.

37
00:05:15,010 --> 00:05:17,070
Yoo Sehyun isn't that kind of person.

38
00:05:17,170 --> 00:05:19,020
What are you talking about?

39
00:05:20,610 --> 00:05:21,950
Whether he is or not,

40
00:05:22,050 --> 00:05:23,670
you're a cop and he's a suspect,

41
00:05:23,670 --> 00:05:24,280
you know?

42
00:05:25,850 --> 00:05:27,270
You two shouldn't get involved.

43
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:28,180
I'm busy.

44
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:31,980
Let's talk later.

45
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:37,540
Gosh, damn it.

46
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:42,680
Hey.

47
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:45,350
Hey! Hey!

48
00:05:48,300 --> 00:05:49,120
Goodness,

49
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,490
you're boring.

50
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:52,280
Got it.

51
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,520
We'll talk later.

52
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,090
Did you come looking for me?

53
00:06:45,250 --> 00:06:46,170
Sung Ho,

54
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,300
it's dangerous here.

55
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:52,750
I'm here to help you.

56
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,010
How are you going to help me?

57
00:07:04,940 --> 00:07:05,670
Kwon Hyukjae

58
00:07:08,050 --> 00:07:09,780
knows about our relationship.

59
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,260
You're in danger here.

60
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,780
I'm not the only one in danger.

61
00:07:19,250 --> 00:07:20,450
You're in danger too.

62
00:07:22,050 --> 00:07:24,050
He's not someone to be trifled with.

63
00:07:24,570 --> 00:07:25,520
Besides, you just

64
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,720
came back from the US.

65
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:28,720
How can you

66
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,550
even help me?

67
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,020
Do you want to be

68
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,720
stuck in such a life forever?

69
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:44,010
I said I'll help you.

70
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:53,610
What's wrong with such a life?

71
00:07:55,420 --> 00:07:56,230
This is

72
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,210
the life I chose.

73
00:07:59,320 --> 00:07:59,780
Sung Ho,

74
00:08:00,970 --> 00:08:02,230
don't come to me again.

75
00:08:04,650 --> 00:08:05,980
Or I'll call the police.

76
00:08:11,220 --> 00:08:13,080
How long are you going to run away?

77
00:08:13,670 --> 00:08:14,980
I said I'll help you!

78
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:25,900
Let's have a drink together.

79
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:28,120
Yeah?

80
00:08:28,690 --> 00:08:29,890
That's a first for me,

81
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:30,460
Mr. Yoo.

82
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:42,919
Let's have dinner together tonight.

83
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:44,750
Sure.

84
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:45,850
Let's go.

85
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,080
Our dear Mr. Yoo,

86
00:09:29,540 --> 00:09:30,890
have a drink.

87
00:09:36,460 --> 00:09:37,460
That's enough.

88
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:10,460
I'm sorry.

89
00:10:10,460 --> 00:10:11,440
I-I was wrong.

90
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:19,820
Sung Ho!

91
00:10:21,180 --> 00:10:22,550
Why are you here?

92
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:34,710
Don't touch him.

93
00:10:45,370 --> 00:10:46,080
Stop.

94
00:10:46,810 --> 00:10:48,180
I said, stop!

95
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,120
Don't touch Sung Ho.

96
00:10:56,410 --> 00:10:57,160
Come at me.

97
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,050
Let's go.

98
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:13,650
Let's go!

99
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:15,810
I'm not leaving.

100
00:11:17,850 --> 00:11:19,120
You're hurt!

101
00:11:36,820 --> 00:11:38,480
Better than you getting hurt.

102
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:23,680
Officer Kwon,

103
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:24,810
you saw that, right?

104
00:12:25,530 --> 00:12:26,330
Ultimately,

105
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:28,530
Sung Ho lost his cool

106
00:12:28,530 --> 00:12:29,790
because of Yoo Sehyun.

107
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:31,280
And Yoo Sehyun

108
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,780
has completely fallen

109
00:12:33,780 --> 00:12:34,820
for Sung Ho.

110
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:44,810
Gosh, what is this?

111
00:12:45,250 --> 00:12:46,060
Hmm?

112
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:54,950
Minho.

113
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,780
Once a person

114
00:13:00,880 --> 00:13:02,880
has something they want to protect,

115
00:13:03,150 --> 00:13:04,750
they will definitely break,

116
00:13:05,690 --> 00:13:06,650
you know?

117
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:10,790
Yoo Sehyun will eventually do as I say

118
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:12,220
because of Sung Ho.

119
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,260
And Sung Ho will

120
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:15,680
abandon his principles

121
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:17,040
to protect Yoo Sehyun.

122
00:13:20,380 --> 00:13:22,040
Then, they'll both be doomed.

123
00:13:24,820 --> 00:13:25,880
Do you understand?

124
00:13:34,250 --> 00:13:36,050
Why'd you let yourself get hurt?

125
00:15:02,390 --> 00:15:02,960
Sung Ho.

126
00:15:11,170 --> 00:15:12,310
Are you OK?

127
00:15:13,850 --> 00:15:14,990
I'm sorry.

128
00:15:14,990 --> 00:15:15,840
I crossed the line

129
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:16,850
just now.

130
00:15:16,950 --> 00:15:17,550
Leave.

131
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:21,480
And don't ever touch Sehyun again.

132
00:15:37,420 --> 00:15:38,080
Sung Ho.

133
00:15:40,450 --> 00:15:41,190
I'm sorry.

134
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:43,960
It's all my fault.

135
00:15:45,660 --> 00:15:47,220
Dragging you in

136
00:15:48,290 --> 00:15:49,610
and pushing you away,

137
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:51,750
it's all my fault.

138
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:57,820
I know.

139
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:00,220
What?

140
00:16:02,650 --> 00:16:04,650
I know who forced you to push me away.

141
00:16:05,990 --> 00:16:07,590
And I know who did this to you.

142
00:16:10,650 --> 00:16:12,280
You didn't want to abandon me

143
00:16:14,380 --> 00:16:15,580
but to save me, right?

144
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:20,420
I wanted you to hate me.

145
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:23,920
Only then

146
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:25,180
could I push you away.

147
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:27,780
Because I

148
00:16:29,220 --> 00:16:30,130
didn't want to see you

149
00:16:30,130 --> 00:16:31,130
get hurt anymore.

150
00:16:33,110 --> 00:16:34,410
But why did you...

151
00:16:36,220 --> 00:16:36,850
You fool.

152
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,770
Why endure it alone when I'm here?

153
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:50,690
Aren't you scared?

154
00:16:53,810 --> 00:16:54,290
I am.

155
00:16:58,070 --> 00:16:59,930
But I'm more scared of losing you.

156
00:17:08,369 --> 00:17:09,349
I'm so scared.

157
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:11,950
Scared that you'll

158
00:17:13,460 --> 00:17:15,060
get hurt again because of me.

159
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,180
Nothing else matters.

160
00:17:21,270 --> 00:17:22,900
Even if I lose everything,

161
00:17:25,710 --> 00:17:27,440
having you by my side is enough.

162
00:17:37,930 --> 00:17:38,560
Sung Ho.

163
00:17:41,190 --> 00:17:42,050
Can I kiss you?

164
00:18:11,810 --> 00:18:12,870
Does it still hurt?

165
00:18:14,520 --> 00:18:14,980
No.

166
00:18:16,730 --> 00:18:18,480
As long as I can feel your touch,

167
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,320
it can never hurt.

168
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:51,000
[Sin and Love]

